PICMI

Manual Installation
-------------------

The following dependencies need to be installed to compile and run picmi:

sdl, sdl_gfx, sdl_image, sdl_ttf, imagemagick

To build picmi, enter the src directory and run

make

To install, run

make install

as root.

By default, picmi will install files in

/usr/bin/
/usr/share/applications/
/usr/share/picmi/


Installation from AUR (Archlinux)
-------------------

Package Name: picmi (old name: tuxpicross)
URL: http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=35212


Enjoy!
